    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155770/extras/8dcf5f315745b28f43e93245873205d0.poster.avif?t=1729698527\" width=600 height=385 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155770/extras/8dcf5f315745b28f43e93245873205d0.webm?t=1729698527\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>A minimalist Tetris-inspired game where the purpose is to fill platforms by moving, rotating and dropping blocks. Once filled, the platform is scored and another one appears. <br><br>If the piece does not fit, the player can drop them on top of existing blocks, or discard the piece completely by dropping it off the side. The game features three game modes:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155770/extras/5c0cda2f30bd4a2f0f755d9abc946983.poster.avif?t=1729698527\" width=600 height=87 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155770/extras/5c0cda2f30bd4a2f0f755d9abc946983.webm?t=1729698527\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Maximize your score before the time runs out by filling as many platforms as possible before the time runs out. Every new platform will grant more time and placing blocks will also grant the player more time. Destroying previously placed blocks will cost the player precious time but sometimes the time saved will be worth it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155770/extras/5597bf447e00fe5bba14188025878d54.poster.avif?t=1729698527\" width=600 height=87 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155770/extras/5597bf447e00fe5bba14188025878d54.webm?t=1729698527\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Maximize your score before you run out of &quot;boxes&quot; (lives). Be accurate and plan ahead. Placing on top of previously placed blocks or dropping off to the side will cost you boxes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155770/extras/63666549578c08478b4e5591832e4e45.poster.avif?t=1729698527\" width=600 height=87 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155770/extras/63666549578c08478b4e5591832e4e45.webm?t=1729698527\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A relaxing way to play where there is no loss condition, play for as long as you want. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155770/extras/5846998c3eba5179faf27e164e74dbae.poster.avif?t=1729698527\" width=600 height=165 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155770/extras/5846998c3eba5179faf27e164e74dbae.webm?t=1729698527\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The platforms and the pieces come in various shapes.<br><br>The game features recoloring options that lets the player customize colors as well as two different background options.</p>",
